        <div class="event-desc">A proper UWS neighborhood breakfast spot on Amsterdam Ave. Big honest American breakfasts — pancakes, eggs, fresh-squeezed juice. Casual, unhurried, kids welcome. The perfect last morning before checkout. 5-minute walk from the hotel.</div>
